====Usage notes====
* Used only in compound numerals, never alone.
* Not used in front of {{m|fi|sadas||hundredth}}, {{m|fi|tuhannes||thousandth}} etc.
*: {{uxi|fi|sadas|hundredth}}
*: {{uxi|fi|sadastuhannes'''yhdes'''|'''one''' hundred '''one''' thousand '''first'''}}
*: {{uxi|fi|miljoonas|millionth}}
*: {{uxi|fi|kahdestuhannessadas|two thousand '''one''' hundredth}}
*: {{uxi|fi|kaksituhattasadas|two thousand '''one''' hundredth}}
* Interchangeable with {{m|fi|ensimmäinen||first}} at the end of an ordinal, i.e. when indicating ones (except with 11th); ''ensimmäinen'' is currently more commonly used.
